fulltitle: Life and Death in the Jazz Business - Coltrane, Brecker and Mulgrew
description:
Solo Transcriptions - The Michael Brecker Collection

Live in Helsinki

Please "Like" "Comment" and "Subscribe" to the videos you watch on the Jazz Video Channel.

Bret Primack reflects on the temporary nature of life, and the eternal nature of the music and spirit of John Coltrane, Michael Brecker and Mulgrew Miller, featuring rare interviews and performances by Sonny Rollins, Michael Brecker and Mulgrew Miller.
